## Quick Reference

- **Project**: Multi-modal voice/text/video AI interface with session management
- **Backends**: Riva gRPC, OpenAI REST + Realtime, Azure Speech (future)
- **Key Features**: Timeline analysis, latency metrics, configuration presets
- **Modes**: WebUI (default) or headless CLI
- **Current Phase**: Foundation (Phase 1) - see [Implementation Plan](../docs/cursor/IMPLEMENTATION_PHASES.md)

## Development Workflow

1. Read relevant rule files before starting new features
2. Follow architecture patterns for consistency
3. Update planning docs when making significant changes
4. Test both WebUI and CLI modes when applicable
